@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@sessionId = {{createSession.response.body.sessionId}}

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Health Check - Live
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/live

### Health Check - Ready
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready

### Get Available Species
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/game/species

### Create New Session
# @name createSession
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game/session
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Session State
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/game/session/{{sessionId}}

### Place Bet on Racer 0
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game/session/{{sessionId}}/bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "racerId": 0
}

### Finish Race (Racer 0 wins)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game/session/{{sessionId}}/finish
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "winnerId": 0
}

### Next Round
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game/session/{{sessionId}}/next
Content-Type: application/json
